## Ignore Visual Studio User and Cache Files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
.vs/

## Ignore Build Outputs
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

## Ignore NuGet Packages (Very Important!)
packages/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## Ignore API Keys and Secrets (Keep your keys safe!)
*.api_key
.env
*.json.secret

## Ignore OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Ignore Bunifu folder (Source code of UI library - optional to keep, but usually better to ignore if it's large)
# Bunifu.UI.Form/